description: Rarely available water-view condo at the base of First Hill, in sought-after building. Just steps from Downtown, Capitol Hill, world-class dining, shopping, cultural attractions & world-class medical facilities. Expansive windows frame sweeping views of Puget Sound, Lake Union & the sparkling city skyline, filling the home with abundant natural light throughout the day. Spacious 2-bedroom layout features engineered hardwood floors, stylish tile baths, generous closets, an inviting open design perfect for entertaining or unwinding. Secure parking, a fitness center, game and activity rooms, & a large community deck with BBQs add to the lifestyle. In a solid, well-managed building, this home is a daily retreat—don’t miss it!
